{"ts":"2026-07-06T08:03:04.192Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/438\n\n## Problem\nNo way to create/update an item from one JSON document: `pm create -` treats `-` as the title; `--stdin` is unknown. Structured agents must translate an item into 10-20 flags; strict-mode errors suggest a 19-flag retry.\n\n## Proposed fix\n`pm create --stdin-json` and `pm update <id> --stdin-json` accepting the same item shape `pm get --json` emits (round-trip: get | modify | update). Flags win over document keys when both given. Reject unknown keys with did-you-mean.\n\n## Definition of done\nCreate+update accept full item documents on stdin incl. deps/comments/files facets; round-trip spec (get -> update) green; SDK/MCP parity noted (MCP already takes structured params); docs + contracts updated."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-kipd"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-438: accept a full item JSON document on stdin for pm create / pm update"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-438: no single-document create/update; agents translate items into 10-20 flags. Duplicate check: searched stdin json/document create — only per-field stdin support (--dep -, --note -) exists; no open overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:04.192Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T08:03:04.192Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":240},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"create/update accept --stdin-json full-item documents incl. facets; get->modify->update round-trip spec green; unknown keys rejected with did-you-mean; docs+contracts updated"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"4ce0cb08f4db481adc74d066cad9a500d8e97f42c9374ac18eb66486d143c26e","message":""}
